# graphify knowledge graph — commit the core graph (graph.json, GRAPH_REPORT.md,
# manifest.json, cost.json) so new sessions can read it; ignore the heavy,
# fully-regenerable artifacts (Obsidian vault, interactive HTML, extraction cache).
graphify-out/obsidian/
graphify-out/cache/
graphify-out/memory/
graphify-out/graph.html
graphify-out/*.svg
graphify-out/*.graphml
graphify-out/.needs_update
.graphify_*.json
.graphify_*.txt
